{"tid":1073162,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［3D異星工廠］Satisfactory 滿意工廠 體驗版","createTime":"2019-03-22T13:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T02:43:36.000Z","uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28c4d15a01736932e60c7396c9d42465b1b9e64b","tid":1073162,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKsVVtG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKsVVtG.png&h=f9459048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Satisfactory（暫譯：滿意工廠）》是Coffee Stain Studios開發的一套冒險沙盒遊戲。本遊戲發布於Microsoft Windows平台，於2019年3月20日在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">EPIC遊戲商店</span></strong>上架。<br />\n<br />\n與《異星工廠》一樣，玩家需通過收集地圖上的原始資源，進行不同級別的合成而獲得各種材料。<br />\n<br />\nE3預告片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5TogHASrCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di5TogHASrCo&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=25cbe1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5TogHASrCo</a><br />\n<br />\n搶先體驗預告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bLhfdULPj8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbLhfdULPj8A&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=1564890d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bLhfdULPj8A</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GiJezCUKvb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGiJezCUKvb4&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=f0432fcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GiJezCUKvb4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">雖然隻Game唔爭氣出喺Epic Game Store，但喺我都唔爭氣買咗。有買嘅巴打可以加我好友一齊玩（id：Yasushii898）</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ca6db3cdefb1871c50e2e006ca97b09246b377a7","tid":1073162,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:20:45.000Z"